with distinct veins R+Sc, R1+Sc, R1, M, M+Cu1, Cu1, Cu1b, Cu1a, 2r and Rs+M; areolet distinct and large; radial cell closed, 3.3 times as long as wide; all visible veins dark brown (Fig. 
