<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.596.5945" author="Pujade-Villar, J" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="109" pagination="65 - 75" refId="B25" refString="Pujade-Villar, J, Wang, YP, Guo, R, Chen, XX, 2016. Revision on Palaearctic species of Periclistus Foerster with description of a new species and its host plant gall (Hymenoptera, Cynipidae). ZooKeys 596: 65 - 75, DOI: https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.596.5945" title="Revision on Palaearctic species of Periclistus Foerster with description of a new species and its host plant gall (Hymenoptera, Cynipidae)." url="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.596.5945" volume="596" year="2016">Pujade-Villar et al. (2016)</bibRefCitation>
to accommodate the new species.
</paragraph>
